    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute perfection for me. It runs like a dream and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s clean, comfy, and totally ready for its next adventure! I\u2019d love for it to go to a home where it'll be appreciated just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
