      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies pride of ownership. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor, expected character marks of a well-loved car, such as light stone chips on the front valence. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is clean and free of tears, the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one, and all interior electronics\u2014including the infotainment system and climate control\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It features a documented service history with recent oil changes, brake inspections, and a battery replacement. The engine starts promptly and runs smoothly, while the suspension provides a firm yet comfortable ride. Whether you are looking for a reliable daily commuter or a weekend tourer, this car offers a premium driving experience. Includes the original owner's manual and two sets of keys.",
